WEBVTT

00:01.257 --> 00:03.005
<i>Previously on Mad Men...</i>

00:03.132 --> 00:04.608
I hope you left us something.

00:06.927 --> 00:10.087
You will be here only
<i>when I tell you to be here.</i>

00:10.188 --> 00:11.372
We're done, Peter.

00:11.475 --> 00:12.693
Have a happy birthday.

00:12.787 --> 00:13.844
How old are you gonna be?

00:14.435 --> 00:15.618
Forty.

00:15.976 --> 00:18.002
So when you're forty,
how old will I be?

00:18.105 --> 00:19.460
You'll be dead.

00:19.913 --> 00:21.398
My boss made a call.

00:21.520 --> 00:23.230
You told Mayor Lindsay.

00:25.628 --> 00:28.982
We have to be careful.
We can't fall in love.

